Why This Is Still Impressive
This is the same architecture pattern used by thousands of real startups. Vercel, Render, and Supabase are all production-grade platforms used by real companies. The fact that they have free tiers does not make the architecture less valid вҖ” it makes you smart for using them. The skills being demonstrated (Docker, CI/CD, REST API design, auth, RBAC, testing) are identical regardless of whether the backend runs on Render or AWS ECS.

